Load accessions file

groups = data.frame(read.csv('../data-raw/TraysAcessions.csv',sep=";",stringsAsFactors = FALSE))
groups$Watering = groups$tray
groups$Tray = groups$tray
groups$tray = NULL

Translate tray name

groups$Tray = gsub("D1", "8.W.A.3.a", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W1", "8.W.A.3.b", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("D2", "8.W.A.3.c", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W2", "8.W.B.3.a", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("D3", "8.W.B.3.b", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W3", "8.W.B.3.c", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("D4", "8.W.C.3.a", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W4", "8.W.C.3.b", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("D5", "8.W.C.3.c", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W5", "8.W.D.3.a", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("D6", "8.W.D.3.b", groups$Tray)
groups$Tray = gsub("W6", "8.W.D.3.c", groups$Tray)

groups$Watering = gsub("1", "", groups$Watering)
groups$Watering = gsub("2", "", groups$Watering)
groups$Watering = gsub("3", "", groups$Watering)
groups$Watering = gsub("4", "", groups$Watering)
groups$Watering = gsub("5", "", groups$Watering)
groups$Watering = gsub("6", "", groups$Watering)

Merge with accessions

groups$tomerge=paste(groups$pos,c(groups$Tray),sep="_")
head(groups)
##   pos           id Watering      Tray     tomerge
## 1   0  SALK_074927        D 8.W.A.3.a 0_8.W.A.3.a
## 2   1          IGN        D 8.W.A.3.a 1_8.W.A.3.a
## 3   2  SALK_141891        D 8.W.A.3.a 2_8.W.A.3.a
## 4   3          IGN        D 8.W.A.3.a 3_8.W.A.3.a
## 5   4         7255        D 8.W.A.3.a 4_8.W.A.3.a
## 6   5 SAIL_247_B11        D 8.W.A.3.a 5_8.W.A.3.a
group=merge(x=groups,y=therm, by=c('tomerge'))
stats=subset(group, id != 'IGN' & mean != 'NaN' )
stats$Tray.x=NULL

Plot raw data

w=ggplot(stats, aes(y=mean, x=Date, group=tomerge, color=tomerge)) + ylab("Mean Temperature") + geom_line(data=subset(stats,Watering=="W")) + theme_bw()
w=w + guides(color=FALSE)

d=ggplot(stats, aes(y=mean, x=Date, group=tomerge, color=tomerge)) + ylab("Mean Temperature") + geom_line(data=subset(stats,Watering=="D")) + theme_bw()
d=d + guides(color=FALSE)

wd = plot_grid(w,d,labels=c("Water","Drought"))

Output

Filter out accessions with less than 2 replicates in either treatment

mediafiltacc = stats %>%
  filter(!id %in% c("9944", "SALK_045606", "SALK_060946", "SALK_107255", "SALK_137176"))

Calculation of means

media = mediafiltacc %>%
  group_by(id,Watering,Date) %>%
  summarize(mediafinal=mean(mean))

Plot mean of replicates (same plot as before)

meand=ggplot(media, aes(y=mediafinal, x=Date, group=id, color=id)) +
  geom_line(data=subset(media,Watering=="D")) + theme_bw() + ylab("Mean Temperature") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1)) +  ylim(18, 25)
meand=meand + guides(color=FALSE)

meanw=ggplot(media, aes(y=mediafinal, x=Date, group=id, color=id)) +
  geom_line(data=subset(media,Watering=="W")) + theme_bw() + ylab("Mean Temperature") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1)) +  ylim(18, 25)
meanw=meanw + guides(color=FALSE)

means = plot_grid(meanw,meand,labels=c("Water","Drought"))
